<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>世纪创投</title>

<meta name="description" content="">
<meta name="author" content="">
<#include "/common/resource.ftl">
</head>
<body>
<div style="min-width:1349px">
<#include "/common/header.ftl">
<div class="wapper">
	<div class="main">
       <div class="reg_index bulk_standard">
           <div class="p-jk">
               <div class="p-jk-box p-jk-box-blue">
                   <div class="p-jk-hd">抵押借款</div>
                   <div class="p-jk-bd">
                       <ul class="p-jk-ul p-jk-ul-line">
                           <li class="tit">申请条件</li>
                           <li>1、借款人需对借款提供房产、商铺、车辆等作为抵押担保。</li>
                           <li>2、房产抵押只对厦门地区开放此项业务、车辆抵押贷款只对深圳开放此项业务。</li>
                           <li>3、借款人须经世纪创投调查人员实地调查并通过审核。</li>
                       </ul>
                       <ul class="p-jk-ul">
                           <li class="tit">必要申请资料</li>
                           <li>身份证</li>
                           <li>户口本</li>
                           <li>征信报告</li>
                           <li>婚姻证明</li>
                           <li>收入证明或银行流水</li>
                           <li>房产证</li>
                       </ul>
                       <a href="${base}/loan/goToLoan.do?productNo=14" class="btn">去看看</a>
                   </div>
               </div>
               <div class="p-jk-box p-jk-box-aqua">
                   <div class="p-jk-hd">担保借款</div>
                   <div class="p-jk-bd">
                       <ul class="p-jk-ul p-jk-ul-line">
                           <li class="tit">申请条件</li>
                           <li>1、借款人需提供世纪创投委托的合作机构、认可的第三方对该借款承担连带保证责任，并签署正规担保合同。</li>
                           <li>2、借款人须经世纪创投调查人员实地调查并通过审核。</li>
                       </ul>
                       <ul class="p-jk-ul">
                           <li class="tit">必要申请资料</li>
                           <li>身份证</li>
                           <li>户口本</li>
                           <li>征信报告</li>
                           <li>婚姻证明</li>
                           <li>收入证明或银行流水</li>
                           <li>担保合同</li>
                       </ul>
                       <a href="${base}/loan/goToLoan.do?productNo=16" class="btn">去看看</a>
                   </div>
               </div>
               <div class="p-jk-box p-jk-box-yellow">
                   <div class="p-jk-hd">信用借款</div>
                   <div class="p-jk-bd">
                       <ul class="p-jk-ul p-jk-ul-line">
                           <li class="tit">申请条件</li>
                           <li>1、借款人职业局限于在编公务员、事业单位编内在职员工、大型国企职员、教师、医生等优质职业。</li>
                           <li>2、借款人须经世纪创投调查人员实地调查并通过审核。</li>
                           <li>3、目前只对厦门开放此项业务。</li>
                       </ul>
                       <ul class="p-jk-ul">
                           <li class="tit">必要申请资料</li>
                           <li>身份证</li>
                           <li>户口本</li>
                           <li>征信报告</li>
                           <li>婚姻证明</li>
                           <li>收入证明或银行流水</li>
                           <li>工作证等相关工作证明</li>
                       </ul>
                       <a href="${base}/loan/goToLoan.do?productNo=15" class="btn">去看看</a>
                   </div>
               </div>
           </div>
    </div>
   </div>
</div>
<#include "/common/footer.ftl">
</div>
</body>
</html>